::Shadow Wing::

She looked at Prowl. "Hey, commander? You alright?" She ran over to 
him. She looked up at the newcomer.  Now that she was grounded, she 
was more vunurable.  she raised her gun up and readied to fire. She 
knew that her gun was no match for missled, but she was ready to try.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Zeus/Prowl::
> 
> Zeus growls as his missile misses its mark. The newcomer turns in 
the air, 
> heading for Shadow Wing. Two more missiles get ready to fire.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Heading for Sixshot, Prowl sees Zeus flying under him. He folds his 
wings, 
> diving at Zeus.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Zeus grunts as talons sink into his back, sending him and Prowl 
falling 
> toward the ground, the missiles that Zeus had shot missing and 
hitting trees.
